ut in thin strips","5 g soy sauce","5 g sherry","5 g cornflour","20 g water","5 g sesame oil, plus extra for drizzling","1 fresh red chilli, halved, deseeded","1 tsp fine sea salt","1 pinch ground black pepper, plus extra for sprinkling"]},{"title":"Broth","content":["25 g dried shiitake mushrooms","15 g dried wood ear mushrooms (see tip)","15 g dried enokitake mushrooms","1560 g water, plus enough extra, hot, for soaking","30 g cornflour","5 g vegetable oil","2 medium eggs, beaten","1 beef stock cube (for 0.5 l)","250 g tofu, cut in small cubes","20 g fresh coriander leaves"]}],"id":"r348716","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-_whmvbAqwto\/XZMy2lyFU_I\/AAAAAAAAaqU\/CThJQvL75-0VJFqc-UoCNoBwJ6WvDS8jQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_OtCGZcADBxm3FS9g.png","title":"Pork and Mushroom Broth","publishedAt":"2018-09-10T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"8 g","fat":"6 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"4 g","calories":"155 kJ \/ 37 kcal"},"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h 25m","10 portions"]}